### Link Dexie.js Development Version to Local App

Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md

After globally linking the Dexie.js development repository, this command allows you to symlink that development version into your application's node_modules/dexie directory. This enables real-time testing of changes made in the Dexie.js source within your application.

```Shell
