### Build Dexie Observable Addon from Source

Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/addons/Dexie.Observable/dist/README.md

This set of commands outlines the process to clone the Dexie.js repository, navigate to the observable addon, install its dependencies, and then build or watch for changes to the addon's source code. This is useful for development or if pre-built versions are not suitable.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/Dexie.js.git
cd Dexie.js
npm install
cd addons/Dexie.Observable
npm run build       # or npm run watch
```

